1.Write a T-SQL program to print a message 'WELCOME TO T-SQL CLASSES
  FOR MY DEAR WONDERFULL BATCHES .NET 27 & 28 ' on screen?
ans:
     declare @message varchar(50)
set @message='Welcome to NIT'
print @message


2.Write a T-SQL program to add 2 numbers
ans: 
declare @a int;
declare @b int;
set @a=10
set @b=20
print 'Value of a&b:'+Cast (@a+@b as varchar)
    


