1.Write an SQL query to display:[acenture interview question]

The department name(use alias 'DeptNAME'),the count of doctors(use alias 'TotalDoctors'),
and the total salary (use alias 'TotalSalary') for each department.
Sort the results by the total salary in descending order

Your output should have 3 columns as given below

DEPTNAME     TOTALDOCTORS      TOTALSALARY


SCHEMA:-
======
        DOCTORS                    DEPARTMENTS
      -----------                ---------------
      DOCTORID(PK)               DEPARTMENTID(PK) 
      FIRSTNAME                  DEPARTMENTNAME
      LASTNAME                   LOCATION
      GENDER                     DESCRIPTION
      DATEOFBIRTH                
      PHONE
      EMAIL
      ADDRESS
      DEPARTMENTID(FK)
      EMPLOYMENTDATE
      SALARY




